		{
			dependencies: ["42D066792F50DF80"]
			description: [
				"After getting a stone pickaxe, the next step is getting iron. But where is it?"
				""
				"Iron spawns in &lGregTech Veins&r such as Iron Veins, Magnetite Veins and Mineral Sand veins."
				"To find these, you'll need to use your prospector and start digging until you reach your geological bounty."
			]
