			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1F872E31D37B2985"]
			description: [
				"Time for your first tools. You'll make them out of iron, but if you have the pacience you can also make them out of wrought iron to get a 50% durability boost! Getting tools out of any material in general will complete the quest."
				""
				"Wrought iron sounds good, you say? Well, to make wrought iron, you'll need to smelt iron."
				"..."
				"&o&4One nugget at a time."
				"&rYeah."
