			description: [
				"This is gonna be the main material of the Steam Age!"
				""
				"&lBronze&r is an alloy of &6Copper&r and &7Tin&r. To make it, you have to crush copper and tin ingots in a mortar and then mix them together by hand. Then, you have to smelt the resulting blend in a furnace."
				""
				"This should be easy if you have played GregTech before &o(which you hopefully should have...)&r or if you at least know how to use JEI / EMI."
			]
