		{
			dependencies: ["52617D85959620CD"]
			description: [
				"It's time for something big.... &oreally big.&r It's time to make a &lcoke oven&r."
				""
				"The coke oven will let you make charcoal and coal coke. It'll also give you creosote oil as a byproduct!"
				""
				"->Coal coke is better fuel for furnaces and boilers. You'll want a lot of it to make steel."
				"->Creosote oil isn't useless either - you can burn it in furnaces and liquid boilers too, and it's required to make treated wood, which you'll need to make a primitive water pump to feed your first boilers with water."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Later, you might also want to replace one of the coke oven bricks with a &cCoke Oven Hatch&r to be able to automatically output the creosote."
				""
				"&oMore later&r, you will be able to make a &lPyrolyse Oven&r, which is basically an electric coke oven that can make cool stuff and is faster."
			]
			icon: "gtceu:coke_oven"
